{"tid":680455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騎共享單車青年　捱撞危殆","createTime":"2018-05-27T07:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T09:12:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e68ed1aa6477740e73232f7f5598ab3d2836617","tid":680455,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180527/20402763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F20402763&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2FuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=85d317d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F20402763&h=b701b8d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180527/20402763</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月27日 <br />\n<br />\n騎共享單車青年　捱撞危殆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180527/large/a0506a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180527%2Flarge%2Fa0506a.gif&h=c7c0d440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■騎單車青年被撞傷倒地，有熱心途人代為撐傘。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名21歲青年昨相約友人到大嶼山租用共享單車郊遊，沿翔東路行駛期間，遭一輛巿區的士從後撞倒，倒卧地上昏迷不醒，有熱心途人上前為傷者撐傘及慰問，事主經送院搶救後情況危殆，的士司機則涉危險駕駛致他人嚴重受傷被捕，警方正調查意外起因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n的士疑切線越車<br />\n<br />\n受傷青年姓李，21歲，據稱他周末相約另一名男友人，租用共享單車在大嶼山四處遊歷。昨午12時許，兩人沿東涌翔東路往迪士尼方向行駛，途至富東邨對開時，一輛由53歲姓連男司機駕駛的巿區的士從後而至，懷疑企圖切線越車，撞倒前方騎單車李姓青年，李當場人仰車翻，彈飛數米倒卧路面，頭手腳多處受傷不省人事，友人見狀停車報警。<br />\n<br />\n據報當時有多名途人圍着青年查看傷勢，其中有熱心人撐傘為事主遮陰，亦有途人嘗試與事主對話，希望他不要昏睡，惟事主一直沒有反應。<br />\n<br />\n救護車到場將傷者送往瑪嘉烈醫院，經救治後情況危殆，需留醫深切治療部。警方到場調查後，以涉嫌危險駕駛導致他人嚴重受傷拘捕的士司機扣留調查，正循路面狀況及汽車性能調查意外起因。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張家豪  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n中大澳門男生　宿舍上吊亡<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n挨餓生病主人突失蹤　新界倉狗坎坷的一生"},{"pid":"9b84a52ec95431c91969d58d080a56288341067d","tid":680455,"uid":47160,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"佢冇還單車會唔會扣哂啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a75800eaf5488fce7c8baadfb9f2cb220fd719","tid":680455,"uid":137941,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b84a52ec95431c91969d58d080a56288341067d","tid":680455,"uid":47160,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"佢冇還單車會唔會扣哂啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cb5e1602562b68fdea8e179a27fe8eec903f1e","tid":680455,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cca0b18c2a760da663fa142cab07843c90018a5","tid":680455,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:01:00.000Z","msg":"DC9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3992a54c10988026eaee0cc7033cba5fdd87cc","tid":680455,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母的士狗"},{"pid":"17e6b9d29d682b652399a81ff86d12217a45c50d","tid":680455,"uid":129622,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"蘋果真係好識寫標題，明明同共唔共享單車無關，又要加落去引人屌共享單車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22554681c5d11d1175a6be32e3bf0186d06a7a99","tid":680455,"uid":42250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b84a52ec95431c91969d58d080a56288341067d","tid":680455,"uid":47160,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"佢冇還單車會唔會扣哂啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:12:10.000Z","msg":"一定要佢賠按金啦<br />\n撞爛架車點做生意"}]}